  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Aqualux Suites &amp; Terme is the ideal hotel for a relaxing holiday. This luxurious hotel gives you a real sense of getting away from it all. Best of all, the bustling centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a> is just a 20-minute walk away so there’s plenty to explore. Much of the hotel was built using ecological materials, so they have a good sustainable awareness.</p>
<h2>State-of-the-art spa</h2>
<p>The Aqualux Hotel is the ideal place for a relaxing break. Its state-of-the-art spa is the star of the show. At over 1,000 square metres, there are several saunas, a relaxation area and various treatments on the menu. It has four indoor pools including; one for children, a hydro-massage pool with waterfalls, an elevated pool surrounded by comfy sofas, and one that connects to the outdoor pool.</p>]]></description>
