  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>State-of-the-art spa facilities</strong></p>
<p>The Aqualux has fantastic spa and pool facilities. Choose from four outdoor pools or relax in the sauna, steam room, whirlpool or solarium. There's even an ice-fountain. If you're looking for a hotel where you can completely unwind, this is the place for you.</p>
<p><strong>Spa facilities include:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Indoor pool</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Steam room</li>
<li>Whirlpool</li>
<li>Solarium</li>
<li>Kneipp bath</li>
<li>Ice fountain</li>
<li>Massages and beauty treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Pool towels and bathrobes are available free of charge</li>
</ul>
<p>The spa is free to use, open from 1pm-8pm. Children may only use the indoor pool until 6pm</p>
<p><strong>Hotel facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Four outdoor thermal water pools including a large outdoor pool with waterfall feature and hydro-massage</li>
<li>Children's pool</li>
<li>Garden</li>
<li>Fitness room with weights and state-of-the-art cardio equipment</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking garage</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
